ny kind of food, even if it happens to be moldy or rotten."},{"version":"pearl","text":"It stops eating only to sleep. It doesn\u2019t feel full unless it eats nearly 900 pounds a day."},{"version":"platinum","text":"When its belly is full, it becomes too lethargic to even lift a finger, so it is safe to bounce on its belly."},{"version":"heartgold","text":"What sounds like its cry may actually be its snores or the rumblings of its hungry belly."},{"version":"soulsilver","text":"Its stomach\u2019s digestive juices can dissolve any kind of poison. It can even eat things off the ground."},{"version":"black","text":"When its belly is full, it becomes too lethargic to even lift a finger, so it is safe to bounce on its belly."},{"version":"white","text":"When its belly is full, it becomes too lethargic to even lift a finger, so it is safe to bounce on its belly."},{"version":"black-2","text":"When its belly is full, it becomes too lethargic to even lift a finger, so it is safe to bounce on its belly."},{"version":"white-2","text":"When its belly is full, it becomes too lethargic to even lift a finger, so it is safe to bounce on its belly."},{"version":"x","text":"It is not satisfied unless it eats over 880 pounds of food every day. When it is done eating, it goes promptly to sleep."},{"version":"y","text":"Its stomach can digest any kind of food, even if it happens to be moldy or rotten."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"Snorlax\u2019s typical day consists of nothing more than eating and sleeping. It is such a docile Pok\u00e9mon that there are children who use its expansive belly as a place to play."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"Snorlax\u2019s typical day consists of nothing more than eating and sleeping. It is such a docile Pok\u00e9mon that there are children who use its expansive belly as a place to play."},{"version":"sun","text":"Its stomach is said to be incomparably strong. Even Muk\u2019s poison is nothing more than a hint of spice on Snorlax\u2019s tongue."},{"version":"moon","text":"It eats nearly 900 pounds of food every day. It starts nodding off while eating\u2014and continues to eat even while it\u2019s asleep."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"It doesn\u2019t do anything other than eat and sleep. When prompted to make a serious effort, though, it apparently displays awesome power."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"It has no interest in anything other than eating. Even if you climb up on its stomach while it\u2019s napping, it doesn\u2019t seem to mind at all!"},{"version":"lets-go-pikachu","text":"Will eat anything, even if the food happens to be a little moldy. It never gets an upset stomach."},{"version":"lets-go-eevee","text":"Will eat anything, even if the food happens to be a little moldy. It never gets an upset stomach."},{"version":"sword","text":"It is not satisfied unless it eats over 880 pounds of food every day. When it is done eating, it goes promptly to sleep."},{"version":"shield","text":"This Pok\u00e9mon\u2019s stomach is so strong, even eating moldy or rotten food will not affect it."},{"version":"legends-arceus","text":"This glutton appears in villages without warning and devours the entirety of their rice granaries\u2014such occurrences have long been counted among the gravest of disasters."}],"evo":{"name":"munchlax","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"snorlax","level":1,"min_level":null,"trigger":"level-up","item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":160,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[]}]},"sprite":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/143.png","shiny":"https://